1
00:00:05,588 --> 00:00:12,512
All things are tied together - the wind, the water, the land, and us.

2
00:00:14,639 --> 00:00:22,147
In forests around the world, plants perform a vital process,
transforming carbon dioxide to oxygen.

3
00:00:26,026 --> 00:00:32,866
Carried by winds across the Earth, the very air 
we breathe travels far beyond these trees.

4
00:00:35,744 --> 00:00:42,584
Together, forests and oceans play a crucial role in this global exchange of air.

5
00:00:50,884 --> 00:00:55,013
A breath taken here connects us to the entire planet.
